hcc_text: Douglaston Parkway is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Queens)
info: At Douglaston Parkway at Hor Harding Exwy Exit Eb and Hor Harding Exwy Service Road South, there were 2 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
